# Design System Enforcement Rules

## 1. Detect Which System

| Signal | System |
|---|---|
| @salt-ds/, SaltProvider, --salt-*, .salt- | **Salt DS** |
| @mui/, ThemeProvider, --md-sys-*, Material | **Material 3** |
| @fluentui/, FluentProvider, --color*Brand* | **Fluent 2** |

---

## 2. Universal — Always Enforce

### No Raw Values
- NEVER use raw hex colors (e.g. #1B7F9E) → use semantic token (e.g. var(--salt-palette-accent))
- NEVER use arbitrary spacing (e.g. 15px) → use spacing token (e.g. var(--salt-spacing-200))
- NEVER use arbitrary radius (e.g. 7px) → use curve token (e.g. var(--salt-curve-100))
- NEVER use arbitrary font-size (e.g. 13px) → use type scale token

### Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Text contrast: 4.5:1 normal, 3:1 large (18px bold / 24px)
- Focus ring: visible 2px on all interactive elements
- Touch target: 44px (Salt Touch), 48dp (M3), 32px (Fluent)
- Keyboard: all interactive elements reachable via Tab

### Validation States — Required on ALL Inputs
- error (red/negative) + icon + helper text
- warning (orange/caution) + icon + helper text
- success (green/positive) + icon + helper text
- disabled (reduced opacity, no interaction)

---

## 3. Salt DS Rules

### Button API (from GitHub jpmorganchase/salt-ds)
- Appearances: solid | bordered | transparent (NOT filled/outlined/text)
- Sentiments: accented | neutral | positive | caution | negative
- Usage: <Button sentiment="accented" appearance="solid">

### Input API
- Variants: primary | secondary | tertiary
- bordered prop for full-border mode
- Validation via FormField wrapper: <FormField validationStatus="error">

### Spacing (4px grid, density-responsive)
- --salt-spacing-100: 4px(H) / 8px(M) / 12px(L) / 16px(T)
- --salt-spacing-200: 8px(H) / 16px(M) / 24px(L) / 32px(T)

### Corner Radius (density-responsive)
- --salt-curve-100: 2px(H) / 4px(M) / 6px(L) / 8px(T)

### Component Height
- --salt-size-base: 20px(H) / 28px(M) / 36px(L) / 44px(T)

### Dark Mode
- Accent text uses accentText token (teal-400 #4CA1C2, 6.12:1) not teal-500 (#1B7F9E, 3.90:1)

---

## 4. Material 3 Rules

- Spacing: 8dp baseline grid (4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64dp)
- Shape: Extra Small 4dp, Small 8dp, Medium 12dp, Large 16dp, Extra Large 28dp
- Elevation: Tonal surface in light theme (NOT shadows). surfaceContainer hierarchy.
- State Layers: Hover 8%, Focus 10%, Press 10%, Dragged 16% opacity overlay

---

## 5. Fluent 2 Rules

- Sizes: Small 24px, Medium 32px (default), Large 40px
- Corner Radius: 4px default, Cards 8px, Dialogs 8px
- Elevation: Dual shadow (key + ambient), always use both
- Motion: Entries decelerate, Exits accelerate, Standard easyEase

---

## 6. Common Violations

| Violation | Fix |
|---|---|
| Raw hex #1B7F9E | var(--salt-palette-accent) |
| padding: 15px | var(--salt-spacing-200) |
| border-radius: 7px | var(--salt-curve-100) |
| Button appearance="filled" | Salt uses appearance="solid" |
| Missing validation states | Wrap in FormField validationStatus |
| No focus ring | :focus-visible outline 2px solid |
| Shadow in M3 light theme | Use tonal surface not drop shadow |
| Hardcoded dark colors | Use semantic tokens that auto-switch |
